message.content: cs.DC, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.ET - The paper discusses a methodology for high-level synthesis (HLS) using modern C++ to improve code readability, modularity, and Quality-of-Results (QoR). This falls under the category of digital circuits (cs.DC) and architecture (cs.AR), as well as software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of C++ for FPGA-targeted code generation, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET).
